# 11. Hoare Partition Scheme

Interview Favorite

### Idea

```text
Pivot = First Element

Two pointers

Left Pointer

Right Pointer

Move towards each other

Swap misplaced elements
```

Advantages

```text
Fewer swaps

Faster in practice
```

