# 12. Time Complexity

## Best Case

Balanced Partition

```text
O(n log n)
```

Example

```text
Pivot divides array equally
```

---

## Average Case

```text
O(n log n)
```

Most practical scenarios.

---

## Worst Case

```text
O(n²)
```

Occurs when:

```text
Already Sorted Array

Pivot = First Element

or

Pivot = Last Element
```

Example

```text
1 2 3 4 5 6
```

Partitions become:

```text
n-1 and 0
```

---

# 13. Recurrence Relation

Best/Average

```text
T(n)

= 2T(n/2) + O(n)

= O(n log n)
```

Worst

```text
T(n)

= T(n-1) + O(n)

= O(n²)
```

---

# 14. Space Complexity

Recursive Stack

Average

```text
