# 23. Common Mistakes

## Mistake 1

Wrong Base Condition

Wrong

```java
if(low > high)
```

Correct

```java
if(low < high)
```

---

## Mistake 2

Wrong Pivot Placement

Always swap pivot at end:

```java
swap(arr, i + 1, high);
```

---

## Mistake 3

Including Pivot Again

Wrong

```java
quickSort(low, pivotIndex);
```

Correct

```java
quickSort(low, pivotIndex - 1);

quickSort(pivotIndex + 1, high);
```

